{"id":595855,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/09/【网络民议】好怕有一天我被间谍了/","date":"2018-09-17T17:42:47Z","modified":"2018-09-18T09:21:34Z","title":"【网络民议】好怕有一天我被间谍了","content":"<p>编者按：央视新闻报道，近日，国家安全机关组织开展“2018-雷霆”专项行动，先后破获百余起台湾间谍案。什么是“间谍”行为？什么样的人容易被策反？发现失密、泄密和窃密情况该怎么办？央视新闻用一图说明怎么识别间谍。随后各地媒体也纷纷演示识别间谍。对此，网友们纷纷表示躺着中枪，甚至有网友表示中了两枪，好怕有一天我被间谍了</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-595856\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/9e5389bbly1fvcaybizk3j20p08zs1l0.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"6475\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/9e5389bbly1fvcaybizk3j20p08zs1l0.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/9e5389bbly1fvcaybizk3j20p08zs1l0-79x1024.jpg 79w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-595857\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/Image-from-iOS-1-5.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"471\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/Image-from-iOS-1-5.jpg 684w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/Image-from-iOS-1-5-300x282.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<blockquote><p><strong>以下评论由中国数字时代收集自网络：</strong></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-595858\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/Image-uploaded-from-iOS.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/Image-uploaded-from-iOS.jpg 1280w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/Image-uploaded-from-iOS-300x225.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/Image-uploaded-from-iOS-768x576.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/Image-uploaded-from-iOS-1024x768.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-595859\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/Image-from-iOS-2-7.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"837\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/Image-from-iOS-2-7.jpg 478w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/Image-from-iOS-2-7-179x300.jpg 179w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-595860\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/Capture-5.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"272\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/Capture-5.png 703w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/Capture-5-300x163.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://weibo.com/u/5417346570?refer_flag=1001030106_\">龙大源</a>：我中了两枪</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://weibo.com/u/1249933394?refer_flag=1001030106_\">顾直</a>：间谍我只服地下铛，看了那么多谍战片，要说小英周围全部是我方特工我都相信</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://weibo.com/u/1046450315?refer_flag=1001030106_\">落叶下长安</a>：来吧，色诱我</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://weibo.com/1906400474\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">馒头的甜味</a>：怪不得贪官污吏那么多，原来都是间谍啊</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://weibo.com/1408855717\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">画家蓝蝶</a><i class=\"W_icon icon_approve\" title=\"微博个人认证 \"></i><i class=\"W_icon icon_panda\"></i>：还真没人策反我，策反我这样韭菜有啥用啊？在墙内啥都不知道，知道的还没官宣的多</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://weibo.com/5237672199\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">the陈杰</a>：不要高兴的太早，据可靠消息，国外势力已经秘密组织了14亿间谍，对每个中国人实行精确打击，谁都逃不了。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://weibo.com/zhuodaoren\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">捉刀人</a><i class=\"W_icon icon_wenda_v2_v1\"></i>：连被色诱的机会都没有，想想就伤心</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://weibo.com/5361739213\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">茶亦醉人不需酒</a>：从评论看，这次央屎的大制作，算是扔水里了。屁民已经上岸了，正站岸上看你们手忙脚乱摸石头呢。再说了，石头最近比较忙，砸美帝脚还不砸不过来呢。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://weibo.com/2197925090\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">飘来飘去8882011</a>：好怕有一天我被间谍了</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://weibo.com/1908590795\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">T_TII</a>：我们的学生在国内就好好的，一出国全身都国家机密了。。。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://weibo.com/5538980938\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">你们最有用</a>：我是部队炊事班的，快来色诱我啊，我把养猪技术全部告诉你</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://weibo.com/2034639767\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Matthew528</a><i class=\"W_icon icon_wenda_v2_v1\"></i>：说真的，抓特务这套路几十年前就已经用过了，我们都抓过，还欠我奖状小红花没发呢，能不能与时俱进来点创新？</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://weibo.com/1225793004\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">韩少楼</a>：一下回到谍战大戏中</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://weibo.com/1876557457\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">626607283111llll</a>：真想被敌特考验一下</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://weibo.com/2184169827\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">键盘侠888</a><i class=\"W_icon_yy icon_yy_travel1\"></i>：经济一退，管控逾强，群魔乱舞了。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://weibo.com/1594752943\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">可可西里20110614</a>：我有点危险,退伍且对当前体制不满</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://weibo.com/1837371917\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">willUOX</a>：我都不敢卖旧书旧报了，就怕哪天出卖了国家机密</p></blockquote>\n","author":1057,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,19168,17016],"tags":[36138,11741,36137,36140,8970,36139]}